    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2010-04-28</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2010-05-12T20:29:32Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Nuclear Energy Research Initiative Improvement Act of 2010 - Amends the Energy Policy Act of 2005 to direct the Secretary of Energy to: (1) conduct research to lower the cost of nuclear reactor systems; and (2) develop and publish on the Department of Energy (DOE) website a schedule outlining a five-year strategy to lower such cost effectively.</p> <p>Includes among research subjects: (1) modular and small-scale reactors; (2) balance-of-plant issues; (3) cost-efficient manufacturing and construction; (4) licensing issues; and (5) enhanced proliferation controls.</p> <p><br> </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
